## 10. Project File Structure

```
toa/
├── app.py              ← Flask server, REST API endpoints
├── turing_machine.py   ← TM engine: states, transitions, step recording
├── run.bat             ← One-click startup script (Windows)
├── requirements.txt    ← Python dependencies (flask, flask-cors)
├── templates/
│   └── index.html      ← Main UI page
└── static/
    ├── css/style.css   ← All styling, animations, themes
    └── js/script.js    ← Frontend logic: simulation control, tape rendering,
                           phase flow, color zones, column indicator
```

